    "text": "Winds: Winds will be South-westerly or Westerly. Wind speed will be (25-35) kmph. Wind speed can increase up to (40-45) kmph at times in the sea areas off the coast extending from Puttalam to Pottuvil via Colombo, Gall and Hambantota. State of Sea: The sea areas off the coast extending from Puttalam to Pottuvil via Colombo, Gall and Hambantota may be fairly rough at times. The other sea areas around the island may be slight or Moderate.",
